ABOUT US
Welcome to TVTGroup, We are one part of Ho Chi Minh University of Science. Your
number one source for all things (Prescription Recognition). We're dedicated to giving
you the very best of our product, with a focus on Finding the medicine, Providing
information, Reminding take medicine.
Founded in 2021 by Mr. Le Ngoc Thanh – an M.A of Computer Science, TVTGroup has
come a long way from its beginnings at Ho Chi Minh Nation University, Vietnam. When
Mr. Le Ngoc Thanh first started out, his passion for “understanding the effects of
medicine” drove them to do tons of research, create a professional team with two students
(Triet, Vu) from major Computer Science of Ho Chi Minh University of Science so that
TVTGroup can offer you an App which can help you to find all the information of your
medicine. We now serve customers all over the world, and are thrilled that we're able to
turn our passion into our App named Prescription Recognition.
We hope you enjoy our products as much as we enjoy offering them to you. If you have
any questions or comments, please don't hesitate to contact us.
Sincerely,
Le Ngoc Thanh
